<TR><TD><CENTER><font color="black"><tt>A demonstration of the most remarkable invention of the age,<BR>under direction of N. K. Barton of the Servel<BR>Electric Refrigerator Company.<BR><BR>It talks and exhibits motion pictures at the same time. See it!<BR>Hear it! It will be worth your while<BR>to come. It costs you nothing.</tt></font></CENTER></TD></TR>
